{
  "video_id": "OWiiA9hXbY8",
  "title": "What are you willing to give up to change the way we work? | Martin Danoesastro",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12787.0,
      "end_time": 17140.0,
      "text": "Have you ever watched a flock of birds work together?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18490.0,
      "end_time": 22756.0,
      "text": "Thousands of animals, flying in perfect synchrony:"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 24142.0,
      "end_time": 25923.0,
      "text": "Isn&#39;t it fascinating?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 27200.0,
      "end_time": 32333.0,
      "text": "What I find remarkable is that these birds would not be able to do that"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 32357.0,
      "end_time": 35339.0,
      "text": "if they all would have to follow one leader."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 36185.0,
      "end_time": 39100.0,
      "text": "Their reaction speed would simply be too low."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 40700.0,
      "end_time": 44594.0,
      "text": "Instead, scientists believe that these birds are relying on"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 44618.0,
      "end_time": 46421.0,
      "text": "a few simple rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 47353.0,
      "end_time": 52450.0,
      "text": "allowing every single bird to make autonomous decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 52690.0,
      "end_time": 54350.0,
      "text": "while still flying in perfect synchrony."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 55275.0,
      "end_time": 58979.0,
      "text": "Their alignment enables their autonomy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 59300.0,
      "end_time": 63168.0,
      "text": "and their autonomy makes them fast and flexible."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 64309.0,
      "end_time": 67521.0,
      "text": "Now, what does this have to do with any one of us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 69248.0,
      "end_time": 75394.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s one way of illustrating what I believe to be the most important change"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 75418.0,
      "end_time": 78314.0,
      "text": "that is needed in ways of working today."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 79123.0,
      "end_time": 82221.0,
      "text": "The world is getting faster and more complex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 82245.0,
      "end_time": 84598.0,
      "text": "so we need a new way of working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 84622.0,
      "end_time": 88372.0,
      "text": "a way that creates alignment around purpose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 88396.0,
      "end_time": 90265.0,
      "text": "that takes out bureaucracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 90289.0,
      "end_time": 94789.0,
      "text": "and that truly empowers people to make decisions faster."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 95591.0,
      "end_time": 97449.0,
      "text": "But the question is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 97474.0,
      "end_time": 98917.0,
      "text": "In order to get there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 100101.0,
      "end_time": 102144.0,
      "text": "what are we willing to give up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 104870.0,
      "end_time": 106997.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, I was working with a bank"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 107210.0,
      "end_time": 110318.0,
      "text": "that wanted to embark on a digital transformation."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 110342.0,
      "end_time": 114770.0,
      "text": "They wanted their offering to be simpler, more intuitive, more relevant."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 115913.0,
      "end_time": 121540.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m not sure how many of you have seen a bank from the inside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 121780.0,
      "end_time": 124894.0,
      "text": "so let me try to illustrate what many traditional banks look like."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 125857.0,
      "end_time": 128943.0,
      "text": "You see lots of people in suits"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 128967.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132204.0,
      "text": "taking elevators to go to their department,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 132229.0,
      "end_time": 136462.0,
      "text": "marketers sitting with marketers, engineers with engineers, etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 137526.0,
      "end_time": 139836.0,
      "text": "You see meetings with 20 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 139860.0,
      "end_time": 142242.0,
      "text": "where nothing gets decided."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 142266.0,
      "end_time": 146300.0,
      "text": "Great ideas? They end up in PowerPoint parking lots."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 146978.0,
      "end_time": 150846.0,
      "text": "And there are endless handovers between departments."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 151658.0,
      "end_time": 154863.0,
      "text": "Getting anything done can take forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 155988.0,
      "end_time": 159408.0,
      "text": "So this bank knew that in order to transform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 159432.0,
      "end_time": 162710.0,
      "text": "they would have to improve their time to market"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 162960.0,
      "end_time": 166240.0,
      "text": "by drastically changing their ways of working as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 166890.0,
      "end_time": 168410.0,
      "text": "But how?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 169710.0,
      "end_time": 172776.0,
      "text": "To get some inspiration, we decided to go and have a look at companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 172800.0,
      "end_time": 174753.0,
      "text": "that seem to be more innovative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 174777.0,
      "end_time": 178666.0,
      "text": "like Google, Netflix, Spotify, Zappos."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 179240.0,
      "end_time": 182839.0,
      "text": "And I remember how we were walking the halls at one of these companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 182863.0,
      "end_time": 184854.0,
      "text": "in December 2014,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 184878.0,
      "end_time": 187685.0,
      "text": "a management consultant and a team of bankers."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 188337.0,
      "end_time": 190953.0,
      "text": "We felt like strangers in a strange land,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 190977.0,
      "end_time": 193101.0,
      "text": "surrounded by beanbags and hoodies"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 193125.0,
      "end_time": 195537.0,
      "text": "and lots of smart, creative employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 196262.0,
      "end_time": 199202.0,
      "text": "So then we asked, \"How is your company organized?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 199808.0,
      "end_time": 201994.0,
      "text": "And we expected to get an org chart."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 202180.0,
      "end_time": 205506.0,
      "text": "But instead, they used strange drawings"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 205530.0,
      "end_time": 209259.0,
      "text": "with funny names like \"squads\" and \"chapters\" and \"tribes\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 209283.0,
      "end_time": 211350.0,
      "text": "to explain how they were organized."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 211779.0,
      "end_time": 215494.0,
      "text": "So then we tried to translate that to our own world."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 215518.0,
      "end_time": 218928.0,
      "text": "We asked, \"How many people are working for you?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 219858.0,
      "end_time": 221509.0,
      "text": "\"It depends.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 221533.0,
      "end_time": 223580.0,
      "text": "\"Who do you report to?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 223970.0,
      "end_time": 225247.0,
      "text": "\"It depends.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 225940.0,
      "end_time": 228125.0,
      "text": "\"Who decides on your priorities?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 228919.0,
      "end_time": 230168.0,
      "text": "\"It depends.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 230785.0,
      "end_time": 232573.0,
      "text": "You can imagine our surprise."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 232597.0,
      "end_time": 235957.0,
      "text": "We were asking for what we thought were some of the basic principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 235981.0,
      "end_time": 237154.0,
      "text": "of organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 237178.0,
      "end_time": 239968.0,
      "text": "and their answer was, \"It depends.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 241404.0,
      "end_time": 243130.0,
      "text": "Now, over the course of that day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 243370.0,
      "end_time": 245548.0,
      "text": "we gained a better understanding of their model."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 245572.0,
      "end_time": 249490.0,
      "text": "They believed in the power of small, autonomous teams."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 249514.0,
      "end_time": 251439.0,
      "text": "Their teams were like mini-start-ups."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 251463.0,
      "end_time": 255690.0,
      "text": "They had product people and IT engineers in the same team"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 255930.0,
      "end_time": 258774.0,
      "text": "so they could design, build and test ideas with customers"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 258798.0,
      "end_time": 261414.0,
      "text": "independently of others in the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 261439.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264410.0,
      "text": "They did not need handovers between departments."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 264650.0,
      "end_time": 267478.0,
      "text": "They had all the skills needed right there in the team."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 269330.0,
      "end_time": 271895.0,
      "text": "Now, at the end of that day, we had a session"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 271919.0,
      "end_time": 273926.0,
      "text": "to reflect on what we had learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 274644.0,
      "end_time": 276549.0,
      "text": "And we had started to like their model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 276573.0,
      "end_time": 280669.0,
      "text": "so we were already thinking of how to apply some of these ideas to a bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 282106.0,
      "end_time": 286272.0,
      "text": "But then, one of the hosts, a guy who had not said a word all day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 286296.0,
      "end_time": 288580.0,
      "text": "he suddenly said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 288830.0,
      "end_time": 290350.0,
      "text": "\"So I see you like our model."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 290590.0,
      "end_time": 291997.0,
      "text": "But I have one question for you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 292941.0,
      "end_time": 295800.0,
      "text": "What are you willing to give up?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 296989.0,
      "end_time": 298731.0,
      "text": "What were we willing to give up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 299627.0,
      "end_time": 303500.0,
      "text": "We did not have an answer immediately, but we knew he was right."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 303574.0,
      "end_time": 306368.0,
      "text": "Change is not only about embracing the new;"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 306392.0,
      "end_time": 309646.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s about giving up on some of the old as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 311130.0,
      "end_time": 313780.0,
      "text": "Now, over the past five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 313102.0,
      "end_time": 315527.0,
      "text": "I have worked with companies all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 315551.0,
      "end_time": 317162.0,
      "text": "to change their ways of working."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 317658.0,
      "end_time": 320979.0,
      "text": "And clearly, every company has their own skeptics"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 321300.0,
      "end_time": 323876.0,
      "text": "about why this is not going to work for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 324581.0,
      "end_time": 326571.0,
      "text": "\"Our product is more complex,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 326595.0,
      "end_time": 329748.0,
      "text": "or \"They don&#39;t have the legacy IT like we do,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 329772.0,
      "end_time": 333156.0,
      "text": "or \"Regulators just won&#39;t allow this in our industry.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 334323.0,
      "end_time": 337133.0,
      "text": "But for this bank and also for the other companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 337157.0,
      "end_time": 338841.0,
      "text": "that I have worked with afterwards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 338865.0,
      "end_time": 340883.0,
      "text": "change was possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 341771.0,
      "end_time": 345400.0,
      "text": "Within a year, we completely blew up the old silos"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 345424.0,
      "end_time": 348414.0,
      "text": "between marketing, product, channels and IT."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 348438.0,
      "end_time": 354510.0,
      "text": "Three thousand employees were reorganized into 350 multidisciplinary teams."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 355241.0,
      "end_time": 358308.0,
      "text": "So instead of product people sitting just with product people"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 358332.0,
      "end_time": 360217.0,
      "text": "and engineers with engineers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 360241.0,
      "end_time": 364320.0,
      "text": "a product person and an engineer were now members of the same team."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 364927.0,
      "end_time": 368480.0,
      "text": "You could be a member of a team responsible for account opening"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 368720.0,
      "end_time": 370557.0,
      "text": "or for the mobile banking app, etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 372668.0,
      "end_time": 375100.0,
      "text": "At the go-live date of that new organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 375691.0,
      "end_time": 378993.0,
      "text": "some people were shaking hands for the very first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 379844.0,
      "end_time": 384106.0,
      "text": "only to find out that they had been sitting two minutes away from each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 384130.0,
      "end_time": 388905.0,
      "text": "but they were sending each other emails and status reports for the last 10 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 389815.0,
      "end_time": 391245.0,
      "text": "You would hear someone saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 391269.0,
      "end_time": 394653.0,
      "text": "\"Ah, so you&#39;re the guy that I was always chasing for answers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 394677.0,
      "end_time": 396340.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 396580.0,
      "end_time": 399481.0,
      "text": "But now, they&#39;re having coffee together every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 400199.0,
      "end_time": 403230.0,
      "text": "If the product guy has an idea, he can just raise it"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 403254.0,
      "end_time": 406873.0,
      "text": "to get input from the engineer who is sitting right next to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 407722.0,
      "end_time": 411352.0,
      "text": "They can decide to test with customers immediately --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 411377.0,
      "end_time": 414950.0,
      "text": "no handovers, no PowerPoints, no red tape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 414974.0,
      "end_time": 417490.0,
      "text": "just getting stuff done."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 418806.0,
      "end_time": 420930.0,
      "text": "Now, getting there is not easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 421636.0,
      "end_time": 423250.0,
      "text": "And as it turns out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 423274.0,
      "end_time": 424950.0,
      "text": "\"What are you willing to give up?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 424974.0,
      "end_time": 427236.0,
      "text": "is exactly the right question to ask."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 428761.0,
      "end_time": 433434.0,
      "text": "Autonomous decision-making requires multidisciplinary teams."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 433458.0,
      "end_time": 436554.0,
      "text": "Instead of decisions going up and down the organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 436578.0,
      "end_time": 438405.0,
      "text": "we want the team to decide."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 438429.0,
      "end_time": 442602.0,
      "text": "But to do so, we need all the skills and expertise for that decision"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 442627.0,
      "end_time": 444201.0,
      "text": "in the team."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 444225.0,
      "end_time": 446174.0,
      "text": "And this brings difficult trade-offs."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 447770.0,
      "end_time": 450974.0,
      "text": "Can we physically co-locate our people who are working in different buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 450998.0,
      "end_time": 453480.0,
      "text": "different cities or even different countries today?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 453504.0,
      "end_time": 455966.0,
      "text": "Or should we invest in better videoconferencing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 456510.0,
      "end_time": 460143.0,
      "text": "And how do we ensure consistency in the way we do things"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 460167.0,
      "end_time": 461467.0,
      "text": "across these teams?"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 462920.0,
      "end_time": 464719.0,
      "text": "We still need some kind of management matrix."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 466487.0,
      "end_time": 472216.0,
      "text": "Now, all these changes to structure and process and procedure --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 472240.0,
      "end_time": 473523.0,
      "text": "they are not easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 474515.0,
      "end_time": 476452.0,
      "text": "But in the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 476476.0,
      "end_time": 479806.0,
      "text": "I found that the most difficult thing to change"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 479830.0,
      "end_time": 481377.0,
      "text": "is our own behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 482961.0,
      "end_time": 484394.0,
      "text": "Let me try to illustrate."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 485216.0,
      "end_time": 489519.0,
      "text": "If we want these teams to be fast, flexible, creative, like a mini-start-up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 489543.0,
      "end_time": 492556.0,
      "text": "they have to be empowered and autonomous."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 493321.0,
      "end_time": 497440.0,
      "text": "But this means we cannot have leaders commanding their people what to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 497464.0,
      "end_time": 499290.0,
      "text": "when to do, how to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 499314.0,
      "end_time": 500781.0,
      "text": "No micromanagers."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 501749.0,
      "end_time": 506570.0,
      "text": "But it also means that each employee needs to become a leader,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 506594.0,
      "end_time": 508746.0,
      "text": "regardless of their formal title."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 508770.0,
      "end_time": 512606.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about all of us stepping up to take initiative."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 514207.0,
      "end_time": 517115.0,
      "text": "Now obviously, we also cannot afford"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 517139.0,
      "end_time": 520233.0,
      "text": "to have all these teams running in different directions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 520256.0,
      "end_time": 523920.0,
      "text": "because that would certainly lead to chaos."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 523703.0,
      "end_time": 528482.0,
      "text": "So we need alignment and autonomy at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 528506.0,
      "end_time": 530193.0,
      "text": "just like a flock of birds."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 531594.0,
      "end_time": 533871.0,
      "text": "In an organizational setting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 533895.0,
      "end_time": 535665.0,
      "text": "this requires new behaviors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 535689.0,
      "end_time": 537795.0,
      "text": "and with each new behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 537819.0,
      "end_time": 540640.0,
      "text": "there is giving up on something old as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 541751.0,
      "end_time": 545752.0,
      "text": "Leaders have to make sure that everyone in the organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 545777.0,
      "end_time": 548945.0,
      "text": "is aligned around the overall purpose -- the why --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 548969.0,
      "end_time": 551257.0,
      "text": "and the overall priorities -- the what."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 551281.0,
      "end_time": 555890.0,
      "text": "But then they have to let go and trust their teams"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 555113.0,
      "end_time": 558211.0,
      "text": "to make the right decisions on how to get there."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 559633.0,
      "end_time": 564968.0,
      "text": "Now, creating alignment requires open and transparent communication."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 564992.0,
      "end_time": 568217.0,
      "text": "But you know how they say that information is a source of power?"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 569189.0,
      "end_time": 570909.0,
      "text": "Well, for some managers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 570933.0,
      "end_time": 575434.0,
      "text": "sharing information may feel as if they&#39;re giving up that source of power."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 576237.0,
      "end_time": 578288.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just managers."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 578312.0,
      "end_time": 581857.0,
      "text": "The teams need to communicate openly and transparently as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 582315.0,
      "end_time": 585976.0,
      "text": "In these companies, the teams typically work in short sprints,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 586000.0,
      "end_time": 589229.0,
      "text": "and at the end of every sprint, they organize a demo session"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 589253.0,
      "end_time": 592373.0,
      "text": "to share the output of what they&#39;ve done, transparently."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 593587.0,
      "end_time": 595237.0,
      "text": "And every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 595261.0,
      "end_time": 597516.0,
      "text": "each member of the team gives an update"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 597540.0,
      "end_time": 599904.0,
      "text": "of what they are working on individually."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 601225.0,
      "end_time": 605992.0,
      "text": "Now, all this transparency can be uncomfortable for people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 606160.0,
      "end_time": 609974.0,
      "text": "because suddenly, there is no place to hide anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 609999.0,
      "end_time": 613568.0,
      "text": "Everything we do is transparent for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 614867.0,
      "end_time": 617720.0,
      "text": "So, alignment is not easy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 617960.0,
      "end_time": 620239.0,
      "text": "and providing autonomy is not so obvious, either."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 621157.0,
      "end_time": 623127.0,
      "text": "One executive at another company"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 623151.0,
      "end_time": 627665.0,
      "text": "likes to explain how he used to be a master of milestone-tracking."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 628238.0,
      "end_time": 632115.0,
      "text": "Now, today, to know how things are going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 632139.0,
      "end_time": 634205.0,
      "text": "instead of looking at status reports,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 634229.0,
      "end_time": 638576.0,
      "text": "he needs to walk down to the team floors to attend one of their sessions."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 638600.0,
      "end_time": 640672.0,
      "text": "And instead of telling people what to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 640696.0,
      "end_time": 642459.0,
      "text": "he looks for ways to help them."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 643000.0,
      "end_time": 644770.0,
      "text": "That is radical change"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 644794.0,
      "end_time": 648396.0,
      "text": "for someone who used to be a master of milestone-tracking."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 649777.0,
      "end_time": 652338.0,
      "text": "But in the old world, this executive said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 652362.0,
      "end_time": 654903.0,
      "text": "\"I only had the illusion of control."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 654927.0,
      "end_time": 660476.0,
      "text": "In reality, many projects would run over time and over budget, anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 660500.0,
      "end_time": 662742.0,
      "text": "Now I have much more transparency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 662766.0,
      "end_time": 666116.0,
      "text": "and I can course-correct much earlier if needed.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 667228.0,
      "end_time": 669727.0,
      "text": "And middle managers need to change as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 670201.0,
      "end_time": 673267.0,
      "text": "First of all, without the handovers and the PowerPoint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 673291.0,
      "end_time": 675839.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s less of a need for middle managers."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 675863.0,
      "end_time": 679728.0,
      "text": "And in the old world, there was this idea of thinkers and doers."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 679752.0,
      "end_time": 681939.0,
      "text": "Employees would just follow orders."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 682554.0,
      "end_time": 686363.0,
      "text": "But now, instead of only managing other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 686388.0,
      "end_time": 689770.0,
      "text": "middle managers were expected to become player-coaches."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 690408.0,
      "end_time": 693348.0,
      "text": "So imagine, for the last 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 693372.0,
      "end_time": 696135.0,
      "text": "you have just been telling other people what to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 696159.0,
      "end_time": 698958.0,
      "text": "but now you&#39;re expected to do things yourself again."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 700554.0,
      "end_time": 702531.0,
      "text": "Clearly, this model is not for everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 702555.0,
      "end_time": 705840.0,
      "text": "and some great people leave the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 705609.0,
      "end_time": 707507.0,
      "text": "But the result is a new culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 707531.0,
      "end_time": 708984.0,
      "text": "with less hierarchy."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 710813.0,
      "end_time": 713116.0,
      "text": "And all of this is hard work."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 714272.0,
      "end_time": 715806.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s worth it."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 715830.0,
      "end_time": 717660.0,
      "text": "The companies that I worked with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 717684.0,
      "end_time": 721983.0,
      "text": "they were used to deploying new product features a few times per year."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 722700.0,
      "end_time": 725600.0,
      "text": "Now they have releases every few weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 725300.0,
      "end_time": 727488.0,
      "text": "and without the handovers and the red tape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 727513.0,
      "end_time": 730272.0,
      "text": "the whole organization becomes more efficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 730296.0,
      "end_time": 733926.0,
      "text": "And finally, if you walk the halls of these companies today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 733950.0,
      "end_time": 736142.0,
      "text": "you just feel a new energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 736166.0,
      "end_time": 740210.0,
      "text": "It feels as if you&#39;re walking the halls of a very large start-up."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 741448.0,
      "end_time": 745329.0,
      "text": "Now, to be fair, these companies, they cannot claim victory yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 745931.0,
      "end_time": 748320.0,
      "text": "But at least with this new model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 748560.0,
      "end_time": 751615.0,
      "text": "they are much better prepared to respond to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 753209.0,
      "end_time": 756320.0,
      "text": "The world is getting faster and more complex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 756345.0,
      "end_time": 758602.0,
      "text": "so we need to reboot our way of working."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 759382.0,
      "end_time": 762777.0,
      "text": "And the hardest part of that change is not in structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 762802.0,
      "end_time": 765427.0,
      "text": "or process or procedure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 765451.0,
      "end_time": 768719.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s also not just senior executives taking charge."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 769394.0,
      "end_time": 772163.0,
      "text": "Leaders will be all of those in the organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 772187.0,
      "end_time": 773804.0,
      "text": "who embrace the change."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 774200.0,
      "end_time": 776495.0,
      "text": "We all have to lead the change."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 777732.0,
      "end_time": 779177.0,
      "text": "So the question is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 780300.0,
      "end_time": 782305.0,
      "text": "What are you willing to give up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 783503.0,
      "end_time": 784675.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 784699.0,
      "end_time": 788387.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}